text: Aurora Pro Patria 1919 is a football club which plays in Busto Arsizio in Italy. The club in season 201011 plays in Lega Pro Seconda Divisione group A. == Name == * 1919-1995 Pro Patria et Libertate * 1995-2009 Pro Patria Gallaratese G.B * 2009-present Aurora Pro Patria 1919 Category:Italian football clubs Category:1919 establishments in Italy Category:Province of Varese
